source.inline: if application "Spotify" is running thentell application "Spotify"if player state is playing thenreturn (get artist of current track) & " ‚Äì " & (get name of current track)elsereturn "Pause"end ifend tellend ifreturn " "

longActionAppleScript.inline: if application "Spotify" is not running thentell application "Spotify" to activatetell application "System Events" to tell process "Spotify"set isfullscreen to value of attribute "AXFullScreen" of window 1end tellif isfullscreen is false thentell application "System Events" to keystroke "f" using {command down, control down}delay 2end ifelsetell application "Spotify" to activateend if

actionAppleScript.inline: if application "Spotify" is running thentell application "Spotify"if player state is playing thenpauseelseplayend ifend tellend if

source.inline: set cpu to do shell script "ps axo %cpu | awk '{s+=$1}END{print s}'"return cpu & "%"

actionAppleScript.inline: activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell

source.inline: set mem to do shell script "ps -A -o %mem | awk '{s+=$1}END{print s}'"return mem & "%"

actionAppleScript.inline: activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell
